description:
A classic board game with an ancient Egyptian flavor and updated rules. Immerse yourself in the atmosphere of the ancient pyramids, where every move is a step towards victory over your opponent. Develop your strategic skills, anticipate your opponent's actions, defend your positions and lead your pieces to victory to checkmate the pharaoh!

In the game, you can fight both with a virtual opponent, who offers three difficulty levels, and with friends on one device. The goal is simple - outwit the enemy, destroy his pieces and seize the throne of the pharaoh. Hone your skills, develop logical thinking and become the greatest strategist of Ancient Egypt!

GAME FEATURES
• A smart virtual opponent with three difficulty levels;
• Unique stylized graphics in the spirit of ancient Egyptian culture;
• The ability to play with friends on one device;

Feel like a real ancient commander and prove that you are worthy of becoming the ruler of Egypt!
